name: Githelper
tagline: Helper script for using git inside of an svn checkout due to git-svn not working on our AIX box.
body:
### GitHelper
My very specialized one trick pony to keep svn trunk in sync with git master so I can have all the goodness of git in my svn work world. 

### Authors and Contributors
@chauncey
